                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1771" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">BL-0014</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10246 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈发树诉云南红塔是依法维权还是无理取闹？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A proper rights protection or an unreasonable action？——Chen Fashu prosecutes Hongta Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曾咏梅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">武汉大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南红塔集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">轻工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈发树；云南红塔；云南白药；国有股份转让</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Chen Fashu; Yunnan Hongta; Yunnan Baiyao; state-owned equity transferring</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈发树是中国著名民营企业家。云南红塔是中国以烟草生产和经营为主业的国有独资公司。陈发树与云南红塔原本在业务上毫无关联，但在2009年，双方因为签订了一份股份转让协议而联系到一起。协议约定，云南红塔将自己持有的云南白药股份转让给陈发树，转让总价为22.08亿元。协议签订后5日内，陈发树便将全部股份收购款交付云南红塔。但两年过去了，云南红塔仍未将云南白药股份过户给陈发树。2011年12月,陈发树将云南红塔告上法院，要求云南红塔履行合同。本案例介绍了本次股份转让合同订立的背景和涉及的焦点问题。通过对该案的分析，不仅可以加深学生对国有企业和国有资产管理体制和相关管理规定的认识，而且可以使学生了解民营企业与国有企业签订合同时可能产生的法律风险，提高风险防范意识。 </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Chen Fashu is a famous Chinese entrepreneur in private sector. Yunnan Hongta is a solely state-owned enterprise with the main business of tobacco production and operation. Originally, there is no business relationship between them. However, in 2009，they are correlated since an equity transferring agreement. According to the terms，Yunnan Hongta transfers its own equity of Yunnan Baiyao to Chen Fashu in value of 2.208 billion. Chen Fashu made the payment in full in five days since the agreement was signed whereas two years later, the equity still has not been transferred to him. In December 2011，In December 2011，Chen Fashu filed lawsuit.The case introduces the background of the equity transferring agreement and the focus issue in this dispute. Through analyzing this case，students can strength their understanding of system and rules of asset management in state-owned enterprise. Meanwhile, they can acquire more knowledge about legal risk in contract signing between private firm and state-owned firm and then raise the awareness of risk prevention. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2009</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《商法》、《经济法》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国有企业产权管理和股份转让</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014-11</td>
                            </tr>
